Qwen Image 8 Steps Ultra Fast.description: This is ultra fast Qwen Image generation with official latest lightx2v LoRA. Only 8 steps and CFG 1 therefore it is 12 times faster than official workflow. Its quality almost matching the official workflow.

Qwen Image Edit Plus 12 Steps.description: This is fast Qwen Image Edit Plus 2509 (like FLUX Kontext) with 12 steps. It supports up to 3 input images and this is an amazing model. We are using Qwen-Image-Lightning-8steps-V2.0 and will udate it when a newer better LoRA arrives.

Qwen Image Edit Plus 50 Steps.title: Qwen Image Edit Plus 50 Steps
Qwen Image Edit Plus 50 Steps.description: This is fast Qwen Image Edit Plus 2509 (like FLUX Kontext) with 50 steps. It is using CFG 1.5 however its quality is still not matching demo examples. I am still in research. I think ComfyUI implementation is still broken. You can reduce steps count to 20.

Upscale Images 2X.author: local
Upscale Images 2X.title: Upscale Images 2X
Upscale Images 2X.description: This is a realism oriented extremely high quality latent 2x upscale workflow that is tested with SD 1.5, SDXL, SD 3.5, FLUX, Qwen Image, Wan 2.1, Wan 2.2 image generation workflows and presets we have. For this to work, set everything with direct apply or reuse parameters, and then do direct apply this preset. E.g. 1024x1024 base resolution will become 2048x2048. It is fully dynamic and uses whatever you use as base.
